data.description: You don't want to miss out on this adorable updated east side home!  Out front is a well manicured yard and fresh landscaping.  As you enter, you're greeted with the spacious living room that is flooded with natural light, has new laminate flooring, and opens up to the kitchen.  The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, freshly painted cabinets, and tiled backsplash.  This home offers three bedrooms all with new carpet, and one updated bathroom.  This home also offers a full unfinished basement.  Step out back to the large and private backyard.  The mature trees give it a park-like feel.
